                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-272-victim2344 t18300415-272-viclabel1502"></join>. My servant, Moore, came to me on the 20th of February - I went and missed a candlestick from the seat in the tap-room; the prisoner was there reading the newspaper - I went and rubbed him down; I felt something hard, and said, "What have you here?" - he said,"Nothing, Sir," - I opened his waistcoat, and found my candlestick.</p>
